law.history: Repealed 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 173, Pt. XXII, sec. 3, effective March 20, 2005; and amended ch. 85, sec. 665, effective June 20, 2005. --Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 530, sec. 3, effective April 26, 2000.

metadata.lrc-note: (6/20/2005). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 173 prevails over its amendment in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85.
